## NOTICE

This repository contains the reference specification of the ECR-VP (Epistemic Coherence Review & Verification Protocol).

It does not include executable implementations, software code, automated systems, scoring mechanisms, evaluation metrics, or decision-making algorithms.

ECR-VP is a structural and interpretative verification protocol intended for the architectural analysis of document corpora.

Modification of the protocol text, creation of derivative protocols, partial extraction for independent frameworks, or redistribution of altered versions is not permitted under the terms of the license.

Application of the protocol to third-party corpora is permitted, provided that the protocol text remains unmodified and proper attribution is preserved.
